ensure a dictionary of querystring params is formatted so that the param name is the dictionary key.
querystring dictionaries from requests sometimes look like this. don't want that.
"queryStringParameters": [
    {
        "name": "contained",
        "values": [
            "true"
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "id",
        "values": [
            "1023011178"
        ]
    }
],
